.Sh NAME
.Nm splicebench
.Nd socket splice benchmarking tool
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Bk -words
.Op Fl t
.Cm copy | splice
.Op Ar listen
.Op Ar bindout
.Ar connect
.Ek
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility implements a relay for OpenBSD socket splicing.
It accepts a TCP connection from a client, connects to a server and
splices traffic unidirectionally.
